name: DOCS_RCVD_EVT_LAST_COMPLD
description: This tables contains information regarding the most recently compiled event list received document.

columns.name: DOCUMENT_ID
columns.description: The unique identifier (.1 item) for the document record.

columns.name: LINE
columns.description: The line number for the information associated with this record. Multiple pieces of information can be associated with this record.

columns.name: LAST_COMPLD_EVT_ORG_ID
columns.description: The unique ID of the data exchange organization that compiled this row's Event List most recently.

columns.name: LAST_COMPLD_EVT_ORG_ID_EXTERNAL_NAME
columns.description: Organization's external name used as the display name on forms and user interfaces.

columns.name: LST_COMPLD_EVT_DOCUMENT_CSN_ID
columns.description: The unique contact serial number of the received document for the last compiled Event List.
